\ul Overview\
\ulnone \
This packages installs OpenVanilla Loader 0.6.1 with pre-bundled input methods. OpenVanilla is an "input method" framework that is able to load various input method modules. This packages also comes with several Chinese input method modules that are popular among users of Traditional Chinese. Extras and additional input methods (such as modules or data files for Simplified Chinese) can be downloaded at our website 
\f1 http://openvanilla.org
\f0 \
\
\
\ul What's New in 0.6.1\
\ulnone \
To change user preferences, now you can simply go to the System Preferences and use the OpenVanilla preference panel. We also have a Traditional<->Simplified Chinese" conversion module, so that you can type Traditional Chinese and get Simplified Chinese output, or vice versa. OpenVanilla is the first IM framework that provides such feature. In addition, OpenVanilla now also does "full-width" ASCII characters that are often needed by Asian users. \
\
