\ul How to Uninstall\
\ulnone \
In case you need to uninstall OpenVanilla, please follow these steps:\
\
1. Remove OpenVanilla Loader from your Input Method settings (in the International settings in System Preferences)\
2. Get into shell (Terminal.app will do)\
3. Use the folloing commands:\
\

\f1 	sudo rm -rf /Library/Components/OVLoader.bundle\
	sudo rm -rf /Library/OpenVanilla/0.6.1\
	sudo rm -rf /Library/PreferencePanes/OVPrefPane*\

\f0 \
4. Reboot (relogin only results in an incomplete uninstall)\
